Your Rights and Choices
Subject to limited exceptions under applicable law, you have the right to access, update and correct inaccuracies in your personal information in our custody or control. You also have the right to withdraw your consent to our collection, use and disclosure of personal information, subject to legal and contractual restrictions.
If you would like to exercise these rights, please contact us at
batprivacyrequests@hearst.com
We may request certain personal information for the purpose of verifying your identity.
